@david kushner THAT WAS UNBELIEVABLE💔💔💔Vilnius, David Kushner in Lithuania singing daylight on his summer festivals. That wasn’t on my bingo card. I couldn’t even dream about THAT
@Nicole Mitchell 
#davidkushner #davidkushnerdaylight #davidkushnermusic #poland #lithuania #vilnius #daylight #concerts

David Kushner's "Daylight" explores the internal struggle between temptation (darkness) and doing what is right (light/daylight). The song highlights the paradox of loving and hating a destructive temptation simultaneously, inspired by biblical themes of human sin, addiction, and the desire for mercy
@david kushner 
@Nicole Mitchell 
#davidkushner #daylight #trend #song #lyrics

"Saving Your Soul" by David Kushner is a song from his album The Dichotomy that explores the intense internal struggle between resisting temptation/darkness and staying true to the light. It addresses overcoming moral failings, temptation, and the battle between good and evil, with the devil acting as a metaphor for negative influences
@david kushner 
@Nicole Mitchell 
#davidkushner #idol #trend #daylight #viral

