"I'm not sure I know what things look like in the capital of Albania on a normal Monday, but I'm pretty sure it doesn't usually look like this."

@The Rachel Maddow Show shares her take on the ongoing protests in Albania over plans for a coastal development project backed by Ivanka Trump and Jared Kushner.

